    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >打造属于你的维京传奇</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >化身强大的维京劫掠者艾沃尔，率领你的氏族。先进的角色扮演机制，让你影响周遭的世界。随着你的每一个选择，政治联盟、战斗策略、对话选项与装备成长都会发生相应变化，让你铺就只属于自己的荣耀之路！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208920/extras/fba1dcd4140fc03cb8a58e3b6359ab9c.poster.avif?t=1754572990\" width=600 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208920/extras/fba1dcd4140fc03cb8a58e3b6359ab9c.webm?t=1754572990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208920/extras/fba1dcd4140fc03cb8a58e3b6359ab9c.mp4?t=1754572990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索黑暗时代的世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从挪威的冰封海岸启航，驶向英格兰郁郁葱葱的大地。畅游广袤的开放世界，狩猎传奇野兽，在这个四分五裂的王国揭开隐藏的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208920/extras/654927a538517e539c399f27a1253705.poster.avif?t=1754572990\" width=600 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208920/extras/654927a538517e539c399f27a1253705.webm?t=1754572990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208920/extras/654927a538517e539c399f27a1253705.mp4?t=1754572990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >体验震撼狂暴的战斗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >双持战斧、长剑甚至盾牌，释放维京勇士一往无前的战斗风格，比敌人更加凶狠无情。在贴身近战中活用战术，或粉碎敌人、将其射成蜂窝，或用袖剑一击毙命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208920/extras/1a08fc562dcbc6732b9e137e3bb32cfe.poster.avif?t=1754572990\" width=600 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208920/extras/1a08fc562dcbc6732b9e137e3bb32cfe.webm?t=1754572990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208920/extras/1a08fc562dcbc6732b9e137e3bb32cfe.mp4?t=1754572990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >发展你自己的居民地[</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造升级各种建筑，包括军营、铁匠铺、纹身铺等，深度定制自己的居民地。为您的氏族召集新成员，打造您专属的维京体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208920/extras/9f5e8c765f4979f4f90f7cdac7824868.poster.avif?t=1754572990\" width=600 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208920/extras/9f5e8c765f4979f4f90f7cdac7824868.webm?t=1754572990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208920/extras/9f5e8c765f4979f4f90f7cdac7824868.mp4?t=1754572990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
